fact.features

Class HillasParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • fact.features.HillasParameters
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    stream.Processor

    public class HillasParameters
extends Object
implements stream.Processor
    Calculate the classical hillas parameters on a PixelSet. Calculated are size, length, width, delta, the cog, and the higher moments m3, m4, skewness, kurtosis each for longitudinal and transverse shower coordinates.
